<p>Travis Wernet is a Certified Dream Worker with the Marin Institute for Projective Dream Work and a Universal Life Minister. He has worked with dreams for many years in mental health settings, private groups and individual practice. He has also traveled to Egypt, leading Sound Healing Ceremonies, and is a professional musician with three albums to his credit.</p>

