    ns1:description """<p>Website: <a href="http://tendingdreams.com/">tendingdreams.com</a></p>

<p>Kim Birdsong was born and adopted in Naples, Italy, and has lived most of her life on the Monterey Peninsula. She was a review editor for the Dream Network Journal for many years. </p>

